PLANT WATERING SYSTEM web plan and flow


frontend:
        HTML
        CSS
        JavaScript

backend:
        Firebase Realtime Database

hosting:
        GitHub Pages

ESP32:
        Arduino IDE (C++/C#)
        WiFi (pass, user), ESP32 IP
        Firebase Client library




WEB features:
        live sensor update(every 10 minutes)
        Mobile friendly GUI 
        Dark or light mode
        Users can add their plant or remove their plant info
        low water alert
        plant health status
        battery indicator
        manual/autoset control
        user subsrcription


